title: 4 Rare 80s Albums [Part 50] Alternative Rock
description:
Four great alternative rock records from the 80's. The Silencers record surely stands out, however the others, though somehow obscure, are amongst some of the finest records of alternative rock that was made back then. Please seed and comment what you think of these bands; if you knew them before or if they are new to you!




Dreams So Real - Rough Night in Jericho [1988]

Naive - Fish [1986]

The Silencers - A Letter From St. Paul [1987]

The Woodentops - Giant [1986]
